Chatham Island(s) lily
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:The strikingly large Chatham Island native forget-me-not when cultivated in gardens; also called giant forget-me-not, and formerly Macquarie cabbage. Myosotidium nobile (hortensia)
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
See:
Pronunciation:
Notes: also Chatham lily
